data.description: Welcome home to this move in ready & spacious Raymore gem! A meticulously maintained four bedroom, three bath home tucked away in a private cul-de-sac. The living room boasts an abundance of natural light, complimented by vaulted ceilings & large windows with views of the generously sized fenced in back yard. On the main level you will find the primary bedroom featuring vaulted ceilings, complete with an en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms on the main level offer plenty of space for guests, a home office, or a growing family. On the lower level you will find an additional spacious bedroom, and a finished walk out basement that leads to  HUGE fenced in yard! The 3 car garage boasts plenty of storage space and room for 3 full sized vehicles, or a boat!
